desc: Shop premium beef and lamb from award-winning producers in Australia, New Zealand and the USA prepared by experienced butchers. From Abu Dhabi and Dubai to Cebu City, get the best meat delivered to your home. Visit us from 17th Jan 2021 at 88th Avenue Commercial Park, Gov M. Cuenco Ave, Banilad, Cebu City!

layout.text: The best steaks, burgers and roasts at the touch of a button. Order and pay online for delivery to your door.
